'''Lycée Montaigne de N'Djamena''' ('''LFM''') is a French [[international school]] in [[N'Djamena]], [[Chad]]. It has ''maternelle'' (preschool) through ''lycée'' (senior high school) levels. It opened in 1977.<ref>"[http://www.lycee-montaigne-tchad.org/admnistration-menu/historique-et-effectifs-menu Historique, effectifs et résultats]" ([https://www.webcitation.org/6Vgd2mPyC Archive]). Lycée Montaigne de N'Djamena. Retrieved 19 January 2015.</ref>

